title: Frank Lloyd Wright House Beautiful Boxed Note Cards
description:
Pen your thoughts in style!  Choose from 8 designs featuring ironwork and Middle Eastern tapestries originally published in Wright's House Beautiful book.  Contains 16 foil stamped note cards and 17 envelopes.  Each card is made of 70% recycled paper.  Printed with non- toxic ink.

Card box: 5 3/4 x  4 1/2 x 1 1/2 in.
Individual card: 5 x 3 3/4 in.
